재료
) } export default TitleAndFilter const Container =styled.div` width: 80%; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 2rem; ` const Title = styled.h1` color: ${props=> props.theme.color.gray}; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; ` const Subscription = styled.div` margin-top: 1rem; color: ${props=> props.theme.color.gray}; font-size: 16px; ` const Filter =styled.div` display: flex; ` const ProcessingContainer = styled.div` &:hover { display:block; } ` const MaterialContainer =styled.div` ` const MaterialButton = styled.div` ` const Processing =styled.form` display: none; ` const ProcessingButton =styled.div` &:hover{ ${Processing}{ display: block } } ` const Material = styled.form` `
